Daily dag triggers everyday on 21:00 TRT time zone. Customer usually publish the data around 20:30. We expect 23 files under the date folder. 3 of these files are master files, 1 is manifest file and 1 is data_feed_info.json file. Manifest files consist of file name, hash algorithm which is SHA-256 and row count of the input file.

data_feed_info.json file contains the DC(warehouse_code) info that the folder belongs to, such as:

{
  "partition_values":  [
    "XZ01"
  ]
